data.title: Nova Fractal - Through Our Senses
data.description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Neogoa returns with Main Sequence Star, the first solo release by Nova Fractal , a newly formed project from Croatia. His debut track ”Perplexed” was featured on our compilation Future Architecture. This release can be described as super-melodic new school Goa trance spiced up with full-on energy. Download Main Sequence Star - http://www.neogoa.net/main-sequence-star

Tracklist:

01 - Through Our Senses (144 BPM) 
02 - Autopsy (145 BPM) 
03 - Common Cold (145 BPM)

data.title: Siam - Colorful Expansion
data.description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Neogoa returns with brand new compilation entitled The Omega Point, a collection of previously unreleased tracks by established artists, all of whom released material on Neogoa and many other labels during the last two years. The Omega Point theory refers to a cosmological mechanism for the resurrection of the dead proposed by American mathematical physicist and cosmologist Frank J. Tipler. Download The Omega Point - http://www.neogoa.net/the-omega-point/

Tracklist:

01 - PharaOm - Rainbow Project (145 BPM) 
02 - Siam - Colorful Expansion (142 BPM) 
03 - Nova Fractal - Connect (145 BPM) 
04 - Trinodia - Deceive My Eyes (139 BPM) 
05 - InnerSelf - Modules (150 BPM)

data.title: PharaOm - It's Alive
data.description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa
► Support this release: http://bit.ly/DG4-Bandcamp
► Download for free: http://bit.ly/DG4-Ektoplazm

The new chapter in the Dimensional Gateway series, Veil Of The Moon, ritualizes the annular Solar Eclipse with Goa trance over three different stages, making for the most fitting soundtrack to this event. Even though it has been more than four years since the last Dimensional Gateway compilation appeared (and in the meantime, the team behind Neogoa Records introduced other interesting ideas and concepts on releases such as The World Beyond, Svemirski Hod, and Celestial Transvibrations), this moment is perfect to return to our own roots and unleash fresh works by some new projects, but also welcome back a few of our contributors from the early days.

Veil Of The Moon offers plenty of darker and acidic vibes, but yet it keeps the melodic aspect present in competent and solid Goa trance form.

Tracklist:

☽ Stage 1: Conjuration Through Three Astral Orbs
01 - Dragon Twins - Illa Tahin (145 BPM)
02 - Veasna - Dendrites (145 BPM)
03 - GoaD - Voids (146 BPM)
☽ Stage 2: Into The Throat Of The Lustrous Spiral We Dive
04 - Clementz - Black Dwarfs (145 BPM) 
05 - GoaD vs. Proxeeus - Acid Implant (147 BPM)
06 - PharaOm - It's Alive (144 BPM)
☽ Stage 3: Driving The Possesed Spirit On Moon Chariots
07 - Proxeeus - Dagon (146 BPM)
08 - Negans - Silver (145 BPM)
09 - Cybernetika - Unknown Entity (153 BPM)
